%description
Calculate common quantitative ethnobotany indices to assess the cultural
significance of plant species based on informant consensus. The package
closely follows the paper by Tardio and Pardo-de-Santayana (2008). Tardio,
J., and M. Pardo-de-Santayana, 2008. Cultural Importance Indices: A
Comparative Analysis Based on the Useful Wild Plants of Southern Cantabria
(Northern Spain) 1. Economic Botany, 62(1), 24-39.
<doi:10.1007/s12231-007-9004-5>.

